26#pragma once
27
28#include "CachedResourceClient.h"
29#include <wtf/Forward.h>
30
31namespace WebCore {
32
33class CachedCSSStyleSheet;
34
35class CachedStyleSheetClient : public CachedResourceClient {
36public:
37 virtual ~CachedStyleSheetClient() = default;
38 static CachedResourceClientType expectedType() { return StyleSheetType; }
39 CachedResourceClientType resourceClientType() const override { return expectedType(); }
40 virtual void setCSSStyleSheet(const String& /* href */, const URL& /* baseURL */, const String& /* charset */, const CachedCSSStyleSheet*) { }
41 virtual void setXSLStyleSheet(const String& /* href */, const URL& /* baseURL */, const String& /* sheet */) { }
42};
43
44} // namespace WebCore
